<div>
    <h1>Antique Watch Collection</h1>
    <hr />
    <p>This website is specially created for tracking of antique watches bought and sold in auction. 
        It contains feautures like adding new watches, editing existing entries and deletion of record of watched that is out of stock</p>
</div>
